      <title>Visa 結果超越了消費者支出彈性的預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/visas-profit-rises-strong-consumer-spending-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週二，Visa第二季度業績超出了華爾街的預期，消費者擺脫了對經濟放緩的擔憂，開始在從旅行到外出就餐等各種事務上刷卡，導致其股價在盤後上漲2.7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/visas-profit-rises-strong-consumer-spending-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 20:12:05 GMT</pubDate>
